        <tbox:linkingPolicy xml:lang="en">See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here.</tbox:linkingPolicy>
        <tbox:metamodelingPolicy xml:lang="en">See http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/tbox -- the same policy applies here.</tbox:metamodelingPolicy>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Sub-ontology / ABox for issue entities. Resource-level issues use tbox:target. Assertion-level issues use tbox:subject, tbox:predicate, and tbox:object to designate the roles of resources in the reviewed assertion.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Ontology>
    


